INTRODUCTION

- Fitter Snacker1 is a small BC-based company that makes healthy snack bars. 
- The company currently does everything using individual independent workstations and paper. 
- Although they have enjoyed success, competition is growing in this sector and they have realized that in order to remain competitive, they need to invest in Information Technology. 
- Fitter Snacker does not even have a web site!!! They have come to you to help them design and implement a client/server environment that will modernize the business and allow them 
to invest in information systems that will make their business processes more efficient.
